<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 03:12:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚洲股市在科技财报公布前扩大涨幅，日元脆弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-23/</link><description>亚洲股市周二延续涨势，受到华尔街的影响，本周焦点转向美国科技巨头的财报，而美元依然坚挺，迫使日元跌至 34 年来的新低。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 02:18:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>Tea shop chain Sichuan Baicha Baidao shares slump 23% in Hong Kong debut</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/tea-shop-chain-sichuan-baicha-baidao-shares-slump-23-hong-kong-debut-2024-04-23/</link><description>中国茶饮连锁店四川白茶百道实业有限公司在首次公开募股 (IPO) 3.3 亿美元后，其股价周二在香港上市时下跌超过 20%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 01:57:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/tea-shop-chain-sichuan-baicha-baidao-shares-slump-23-hong-kong-debut-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛面临选举结果的紧张等待</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-faces-tense-wait-election-results-2024-04-22/</link><description>所罗门群岛面临着选举结果的紧张等待，因为反对党领先于现任总理马内塞·索加瓦雷领导的我们党，周二的计票结果显示，独立人士将是组建政府的关键。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 23:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-faces-tense-wait-election-results-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>美国和韩国本周将就美军费用举行会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-south-korea-meet-american-troop-costs-this-week-2024-04-22/</link><description>美国国务院周一表示，美国和韩国官员将于本周在夏威夷会面，就分担驻韩美军的费用进行会谈，美国寻求“公平公正的结果”，以加强两国的联盟。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 22:04:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-south-korea-meet-american-troop-costs-this-week-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：科技行业平静，4 月份 PMI 开始滚动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-22/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 21:59:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称朝鲜进行首次“核触发”模拟演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-guides-nuclear-counterattack-simulation-drills-kcna-says-2024-04-22/</link><description>朝鲜国家通讯社朝中社周二表示，朝鲜在领导人金正恩的指导下进行了首次核反击演习，以模拟其“核触发”管理系统，这是对其敌人的明确警告。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 21:37:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-guides-nuclear-counterattack-simulation-drills-kcna-says-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普称拜登将对任何 TikTok 禁令“负责”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-biden-would-be-responsible-any-tiktok-ban-2024-04-22/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普周一表示，总统乔·拜登正在“推动”对 TikTok 的禁令，如果实施禁令，他将承担责任，并敦促选民注意。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 20:18:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-biden-would-be-responsible-any-tiktok-ban-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾发生6.3级地震，目前尚无受损报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-rattled-by-63-magnitude-quake-no-immediate-reports-damage-2024-04-22/</link><description>台湾气象部门表示，周二，台湾东部花莲县发生了 6.3 级地震，目前尚未收到受损情况报告。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 18:48:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-rattled-by-63-magnitude-quake-no-immediate-reports-damage-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯访华前报告称新疆种族灭绝仍在继续</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-says-genocide-xinjiang-is-ongoing-report-ahead-china-visit-2024-04-22/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯在本周计划访问中国之前发表的一份报告中表示，北京继续在西部新疆省对维吾尔族和其他穆斯林少数民族犯下种族灭绝和反人类罪。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 18:02:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-says-genocide-xinjiang-is-ongoing-report-ahead-china-visit-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：随着石油制裁的回归，委内瑞拉将加速加密货币转型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/venezuela-accelerate-cryptocurrency-shift-oil-sanctions-return-2024-04-22/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，随着美国重新对该国实施石油制裁，委内瑞拉国营石油公司 PDVSA 计划增加其原油和燃料出口中数字货币的使用。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 16:19:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/venezuela-accelerate-cryptocurrency-shift-oil-sanctions-return-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟威胁暂停 TikTok Lite 的奖励计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-lites-reward-programme-may-be-suspended-europe-eu-regulators-say-2024-04-22/</link><description>欧盟委员会周一表示，如果 TikTok 无法解决其可能对儿童造成成瘾影响的担忧，欧盟委员会周四可能会暂停 TikTok Lite 的奖励计划，同时对这款新应用程序在法国和西班牙的推出展开调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:58:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-lites-reward-programme-may-be-suspended-europe-eu-regulators-say-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>美国旅游业等待中国旅游业创2019年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-travel-sector-faces-long-wait-china-tourism-hit-2019-highs-2024-04-22/</link><description>由于中国经济增长缓慢和成本高昂，导致游客远离美国，美国旅游业至少还需要等待两年，利润丰厚的中国旅游业才能恢复到疫情前的水平。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:28:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-travel-sector-faces-long-wait-china-tourism-hit-2019-highs-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉股价因盈利前降价而暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-drop-price-cuts-run-up-earnings-2024-04-22/</link><description>特斯拉周一暴跌 4%，其最新的全球降价举措引发了华尔街对这家电动汽车制造商在本周晚些时候发布财报之前利润率下降的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:03:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-drop-price-cuts-run-up-earnings-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>英国警方指控两名男子为中国从事间谍活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-prosecutors-authorise-charges-against-two-men-over-spying-china-2024-04-22/</link><description>英国警方周一指控两名男子为中国从事间谍活动，其中一名男子据称曾在英国议会为执政的保守党一位著名议员担任研究员。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:47:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-prosecutors-authorise-charges-against-two-men-over-spying-china-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>由于主要市场疲软，印度成品钻石出口下降 27.5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-polished-diamond-exports-drop-275-key-markets-falter-2024-04-22/</link><description>一家主要贸易机构周一表示，由于美国、中国和阿联酋的需求低迷，印度 2023/24 年切割和成品钻石出口额同比下降 27.5%，至 159.7 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:38:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-polished-diamond-exports-drop-275-key-markets-falter-2024-04-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>